<section id="ai-work" class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4">AI & Automation</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Building automation systems, fine-tuning language models, and shipping bots that solve real problems — not experiments. I focus on measurable impact and reliable production deployments.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <article class="ai-card">
        <div class="ai-icon">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Automation Pipelines</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400">Connect tools and services to automate repetitive work, reduce errors, and save time. Cron jobs, event-driven workflows, and monitored pipelines.</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 text-slate-300 space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li>• Orchestrated ETL and data syncs</li>
          <li>• Scheduled jobs & webhooks</li>
          <li>• Monitoring & alerting (SLO-aware)</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="mt-4 inline-block text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Ask about automation →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="ai-card">
        <div class="ai-icon">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">LLM Fine-Tuning</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400">Fine-tune models (LoRA/QLoRA) for domain-specific tasks, improve relevance, and reduce hallucinations through careful data curation and evaluation.</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 text-slate-300 space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li>• Dataset curation & labeling</li>
          <li>• Cost-optimized fine-tuning</li>
          <li>• Evaluation & deployment</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="mt-4 inline-block text-amber-400 font-semibold">Discuss fine-tuning →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="ai-card">
        <div class="ai-icon">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 8h10M7 12h4m1 8a4 4 0 01-4-4V7a4 4 0 118 0v9a4 4 0 01-4 4z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Custom Bots</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400">Build chatbots, automation bots, and agents that integrate with your systems and provide reliable, auditable behaviors.</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 text-slate-300 space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li>• Slack/Teams/Bots</li>
          <li>• Data-aware assistants</li>
          <li>• Secure deployment & monitoring</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="mt-4 inline-block text-purple-400 font-semibold">Let's build a bot →</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .ai-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(15,23,42,0.85), rgba(2,6,23,0.85));
      border-radius: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(100,116,139,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(2,6,23,0.6);
    }

    .ai-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; display: grid; place-items: center; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

    .ai-card h3 { margin-top: 0.25rem; }

    .ai-card a { display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .ai-card { padding: 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</section>